data.text:
Happy February!

Here are three of my favorite Jimmy Bryant guitar solos; Cotton Pickin’, Yodeling Guitar, and Flippin the Lid.

Each solo is jam packed with Jimmy’s signature sounds; chromatic runs, double stops, open string licks, whole tone lines, triple stops, steel guitar emulation, and altered sounding chords/lines.

These three solos can be purchased in PDF/GuitarPro form for $35 total. Upon or after purchase, you can book an hour long Skype lesson ($15 off my normal price of $65 for those who purchase) with me where we take a look at these solos and how to incorporate Jimmy’s ideas into your playing!

All purchases are through paypal…click here!

Any questions? Feel free to contact me.

Happy Pickin!

Ment Morris
